source: crates/cli/tests/cli_output_snapshots.rs
expression: stdout
---
Plugin management commands

Usage: wheelctl.exe plugin [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  list       List available plugins from registry
  search     Search for plugins by name or description
  install    Install a plugin from the registry
  uninstall  Uninstall a plugin
  info       Show detailed plugin information
  verify     Verify an installed plugin's integrity and signature
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --json        Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -v, --verbose...  Verbose logging
  -h, --help        Print help
